OL,4,CFace masks expected to be no longer
OL,5,Crequired in classrooms
OL,6, The wearing of face masks in secondary
OL,7, school classrooms in England will not
OL,8, be required after 17 May, the
OL,9, government is expected to confirm.
OL,11,FFace coverings have been recommended
OL,12,Fsince the return to school in March -
OL,13,Fbut that will end as part of the
OL,14,Fphasing out of lockdown measures.
OL,16,FThere have been concerns masks get in
OL,17,Fthe way of communicating and learning.
OL,19,FBut a group of scientists and teachers'
OL,20,Funions has argued masks should stay to
OL,21,F"keep school students and staff safe".
